<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you two.</font>

343
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck are you doing?</font>

344
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nothing.</font>

345
00:19:13,250 --> 00:19:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's none of your business.</font>

346
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's definitely something afoot.</font>

347
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look so unamused.</font>

348
00:19:22,970 --> 00:19:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a festival, you know?</font>

349
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, come on, come on!</font>

350
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

351
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with you two?</font>

352
00:19:30,580 --> 00:19:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have some fun!</font>

353
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

354
00:19:34,810 --> 00:19:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, what do you wanna do?</font>

355
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pinball?</font>

356
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goldfish scooping?</font>

357
00:19:43,360 --> 00:19:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's let loose and enjoy the festival!</font>

358
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with you all of a sudden, Eiyu?</font>

359
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all hyped up now.</font>

360
00:19:50,250 --> 00:19:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What do you mean? 
This is a festival!</font>

361
00:19:53,710 --> 00:19:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

362
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still don't get it.</font>

363
00:19:55,970 --> 00:19:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Eiyu?</font>

364
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a festival! Woohoo!</font>

365
00:20:01,690 --> 00:20:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on, what's going on?!</i></font>

366
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's something off about them today.</i></font>

367
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's with this tension?</i></font>

368
00:20:08,770 --> 00:20:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's with their gaze?</i></font>

369
00:20:10,650 --> 00:20:13,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know... I don't understand...</i></font>

370
00:20:13,150 --> 00:20:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get anything at all!</i></font>

371
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Festivals are the <i>best</i>!</font>

372
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

373
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

374
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay.</font>

375
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh!</font>

376
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why are you laughing?</font>

377
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... I don't know...</font>

378
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... But it feels nostalgic.</font>

379
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The eight o'clock fireworks show 
will start in an hour.</i></font>

380
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, what should we do next?</font>

381
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We hope you are enjoying the festival.</i></font>

382
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! This isn't the time to be sentimental!</i></font>

383
00:20:48,410 --> 00:20:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu.</font>

384
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

385
00:20:50,470 --> 00:20:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

386
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... c-can we...</font>

387
00:20:56,340 --> 00:20:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hungry?</font>

388
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go! Have this pork skewer!</font>

389
00:21:03,250 --> 00:21:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Thanks!</font>

390
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I said! Gosh!</font>

391
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

392
00:21:10,300 --> 00:21:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just listen, okay?!</font>

393
00:21:13,210 --> 00:21:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The both of us...</font>

394
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

395
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just the two of us...</font>

396
00:21:20,570 --> 00:21:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akarin...</font>

397
00:21:21,730 --> 00:21:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just the two...?</font>

398
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it, you two want to 
let loose without me.</font>

399
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

400
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

401
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

402
00:21:38,170 --> 00:21:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to watch the fireworks 
with just you, Eiyu!</font>

403
